OL,3,CPatients moved to other hospitals
OL,4,Cfollowing fire at Southampton General
OL,6,FSome patients have been moved to other
OL,7,Fhospitals following a fire at
OL,8,FSouthampton General Hospital.
OL,10,FThe fire broke out in the West Wing
OL,11,Fyesterday morning (Sunday 1 February)
OL,12,Fwith University Hospital Southampton
OL,13,Fremaining in a major incident today.
OL,15,FApproximately 200 patients were moved
OL,16,Fto safe areas of the hospital
OL,17,Fincluding corridor spaces during the
OL,18,Femergency.
