OL,6,FIn a statement, University Hospital
OL,7,FSouthampton (UHS), said: "Following a
OL,8,Fconsiderable effort throughout
OL,9,Fyesterday in repurposing all available
OL,10,Fspace in our hospitals, last night all
OL,11,Fof those patients were being cared for
OL,12,Fin beds and on wards.
OL,14,F"The majority remained in Southampton
OL,15,FGeneral Hospital, but some patients
OL,16,Fwere transported to hospitals across
OL,17,Fthe area last night in a coordinated
OL,18,Fmutual aid response with healthcare
OL,19,Fpartners and supported by SCAS.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
