OL,6,F"We would like to thank all our
OL,7,Fpartners and the hospitals who helped
OL,8,Fmake this possible ` we are extremely
OL,9,Fgrateful for their support."
OL,11,FFollowing approval from Hampshire Fire
OL,12,Fand Rescue Service and staff efforts,
OL,13,Fteams have been able to access,
OL,14,Fventilate and clean some areas of the
OL,15,Faffected West Wing wards and safely
OL,16,Fmove a number of patients back there.
OL,18,FThe fire means some patients who had
OL,19,Fto be moved are without their personal
OL,20,Fbelongings, including mobile phones.
