OL,6,FUHS said: "We understand the anxiety
OL,7,Fthis is causing relatives and want to
OL,8,Freassure them we have a dedicated team
OL,9,Fof staff in our Patient Support Hub
OL,10,Fworking to recover belongings when it
OL,11,Fis safe to do so and make contact with
OL,12,Fnext of kin."
OL,14,FThe hospital's Emergency Department
OL,15,Fremains closed this morning unless
OL,16,Fpeople's condition is life or limb
OL,17,Fthreatening.
OL,19,FVisiting has resumed as normal with
OL,20,Fpeople being urged to check visiting
OL,21,Fhours with the ward.
