OL,6,FHowever, a significant amount of
OL,7,Fplanned elective surgery and some
OL,8,Foutpatient appointments have been
OL,9,Fcancelled.
OL,11,FPatients who have been affected have
OL,12,Fbeen contacted directly.
OL,14,FAnybody who has an appointment and has
OL,15,Fnot been contacted, should attend the
OL,16,Fhospital as planned.
