OL,6,FThe trust added: "We would like to
OL,7,Ftake this opportunity to recognise the
OL,8,Fheroic efforts of our staff in the
OL,9,Fimmediate aftermath of yesterday's
OL,10,Ffire, in particular those who swiftly
OL,11,Fmoved patients to safety when the fire
OL,12,Fbroke out.
OL,14,F"The situation has been extremely
OL,15,Fchallenging and we are continuing to
OL,16,Fwork with partners as we continue to
OL,17,Fprioritise safe patient care."
